$ %USERPROFILE%\NTUSER.DAT

`NTUSER.DAT` is a → Windows/registry[registry] hive and part of a *→ Windows/user-account[user] profile*.

When a → Windows/user-account[user] logs on, this registry hive is mapped to → Windows/registry/tree/HKEY_CURRENT_USER[`HKEY_CURRENT_USER`].

? Apparenty, `NTUSER.DAT` also records a user's activities such as
  • accessed files
  • searches
  • network connections
  • launched applications

